{"tid":1667972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1021朝早疑似有手足比人斬，點解無人講！","createTime":"2019-10-21T17:40:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T18:18:50.000Z","uid":192367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9f1b97255883438f71ecdee5ee45b69b5e297ebc","tid":1667972,"uid":192367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:40:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://larid.hk/view22/21548/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flarid.hk%2Fview22%2F21548%2F&d=bp2T%2F%2B5c5q8hcpZmRI3qNstxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=e9addb5c\" target=\"_blank\">http://larid.hk/view22/21548/</a><br />\n<br />\n尖沙嘴柯士甸道112號對開，早上7時14分，姓梁（22歲）青年遭3名兇徒狂斬，頭及身體多處中刀，不支倒在一間髮廊門外，由途人代為報警。警方趕至時，逞兇者已逃去無蹤。現場滿地鮮血，由救護員替傷者包紮，他清醒獲送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n警員圍封現場，大批探員到場，在附近翻看cctv追緝疑人。警方正了解事主身份及遇襲原因。<br />\n<br />\n現場有車CAM拍攝到，逞兇者乘深色私家車到達，兩人落車會合同黨，3人向事主揮刀狂斬。事主毫無反抗能力，倒地捱斬，直至逞兇者逃去，他才一拐一拐地站起身來，但走到行人路上已不支倒地。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇人知佢點呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b33016f5eafd3623ff4eb77dfe3fe02fd8824a44","tid":1667972,"uid":192367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:41:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af235ba34befd13b94625551c939ee7b742ad21e","tid":1667972,"uid":192367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:41:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d53c5b36c31e0f8d7e788d26816bba82a59bc618","tid":1667972,"uid":192367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:41:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c701ffc61ea2f602b1a9c998e950314db52247e6","tid":1667972,"uid":192367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:41:39.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"1055ba69f8ddfaaca21bcd56c95f7b43a2846785","tid":1667972,"uid":192367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:41:49.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"c60e8f18dc0687c4a9fb6c1b47fe26fee9463d84","tid":1667972,"uid":309045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:41:59.000Z","msg":"有post講"},{"pid":"5402cd2e9c8d4f5e6ff0a44574ac8738edf59d87","tid":1667972,"uid":192367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:42:01.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"638e816c0241aa28407bf37abcb2cd34c7e25ea1","tid":1667972,"uid":192367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c60e8f18dc0687c4a9fb6c1b47fe26fee9463d84","tid":1667972,"uid":309045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:41:59.000Z","msg":"有post講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:42:25.000Z","msg":"有冇link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"671254017347b806aed00009d8b6e7ef2b72adeb","tid":1667972,"uid":192367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c60e8f18dc0687c4a9fb6c1b47fe26fee9463d84","tid":1667972,"uid":309045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:41:59.000Z","msg":"有post講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:42:52.000Z","msg":"有我就唔推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15494a06cb5bab1ae2795acff873961797ea52ae","tid":1667972,"uid":309045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:43:57.000Z","msg":"有圖 今日有22歲黑衫年青人係尖沙咀被狂斬 無人講？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1667523-\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1667523-</a> 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4bdaa805930d14b6f1bbe4e8e48969d30cf2991d","tid":1667972,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:52:16.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"a548283d619055f7efd3365a7115f399775f884a","tid":1667972,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:18:50.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"}]}